Geneviève Joyce Waïte (13 Febụwarị 1948 - 18 Mee 2019) bụ onye South Africa na-eme ihe nkiri, onye na-agụ egwu na onye nlereanya. Ọrụ ya a kacha mara amara bụ onye isi na ihe nkiri 1968 Joanna Dị ka onye na-ese onyinyo, Richard Avedon sere ya foto maka Vogue na 1971. N'afọ 1974, o dekọrọ abọm ya dị ka onye na-agụ egwu.

Waïte lụrụ Matthew Reich na 10 Disemba 1968; Ha mechara gbaa alụkwaghịm. Waïte lụrụ onye egwu John Phillips nke Mamas & the Papas na 31 Jenụwarị 1972. Ha nwere ụmụ abụọ: ndị na-eme ihe nkiri Tamerlane Phillips (b
Ọ lụrụ Norman Buntaine; ha mechara kewaa.
Ọ bụ di ya nke abụọ, John Phillips, onye bụbu onye otu egwu Mamas & the Papas mepụtara abọm Waïte nke afọ 1974
N'afọ 2011, e wepụtara abọm ahụ na CD nke gụnyere mkpuchi egwu Velvet Underground "Femme Fatale".
Na 18 Mee 2019, Waïte nwụrụ mgbe ọ na-ehi ura na Los Angeles, California
Nwa ya nwanyị, Bijou, mara ọkwa ọnwụ nne ya ọtụtụ ụbọchị ka e mesịrị.
